        <para id="id65193">Balance the following equations:</para>
        <list id="id65199" display="block" list-type="enumerated"><item id="uid17">Hydrogen fuel cells are extremely important in the development of alternative energy sources. Many of these cells work by reacting hydrogen and oxygen gases together to form water, a reaction which also produces electricity. Balance the following equation:
H<sub>2</sub>(g) + O<sub>2</sub>(g)<m:math><m:mo>→</m:mo></m:math> H<sub>2</sub>O(l)<space/><link window="new" class="fullmarks" resource="http://www.fhsst.org/lOg">Click here for the solution</link></item>
