N<sub>2</sub>(g) + H<sub>2</sub>(g)<m:math><m:mo>→</m:mo></m:math>NH<sub>3</sub>(g)<space/><link window="new" class="fullmarks" resource="http://www.fhsst.org/lO4">Click here for the solution</link></item>
